Overview

This repository contains the Selection Control assignments completed as part of the Infosys Springboard Programming Using Java course.
The assignments focus on using decision-making constructs in Java such as:

if statements

if-else statements

Nested if statements

switch-case statements

These exercises are designed to enhance problem-solving skills and strengthen the understanding of control flow in Java.
